data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of a secure gated community. This exquisite 4/5 Colonial-style residence has been meticulously updated. Offering the perfect blend of modern luxury and timeless charm it makes the best year round home or and exceptional vacation/rental property. With spacious living areas, new state-of-the-art HVAC cooling and heating systems, and a custom-designed kitchen, this property is an absolute gem!! DO NOT miss this  opportunity. Call today to set up an appointment.
